:"m45","userName":"M45","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">陈苦瓜エロゲーマー</span> 说: 你看他在知乎上的文章就知道了</q></div>不用知乎+孤陋寡闻<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/07/310722.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1356377","time":"2018-6-18 01:28","userId":"maple_5233","userName":"桜小路ルナ","userSign":"(大変に気分がいい)","message":"倾尽一生都做不到的.jpg","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/44/14488.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1356390","time":"2018-6-18 01:42","userId":"sengohanabi","userName":"線香花火","userSign":"(Say A Little Prayer)","message":"我现在只看高分了，何苦虐自己去看些烂片浪费时间呢","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1356392","time":"2018-6-18 01:42","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"(｡´-д-)","message":"呃 学习难道不是因为对知识感兴趣 想了解世界掌握技能才学的吗..<br><br>其实也是我遇到的问题..以前觉得这个不行那个也不行..<br>后来发现不是别人不行是自己不行..然后就发现这个很棒那个也很棒..越来越想穷尽一切..<br>再后来发现好作品出得比自己看得还快..<br>算了算了 吾生也有涯, 而番也无涯..以有涯随无涯, 殆已..<br>回忆一下五年前的番剧 有多少是到现在仍然有印象的..时间会帮我们筛选出精品的..<br><br><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">然而筛出来的仍然看不完 更不用说各种漫画游戏..而且那些被筛掉的作品换个说法就成了[埋藏在历史长河中的宝藏]..毕竟人家可是一群人拼了命地摸索和创作..你一个人花个几分钟怎么可能穷尽呢..如果关注细节的话 每一部作品都有其独一无二的特点..甚至那些最烂的作品 都可能只是一次失败的尝试..是在为下一次成功铺路..</span><br><br>时间不允许 那也只能舍弃掉了啊..提高自己的标准 或者让大家的评价帮你做选择..毕竟一部作品喜欢的人越多意味着它的优点越多短板越少..<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">然而有时候大众的选择又不靠谱</span><br><br><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">但是真能做到么? 不是许多人宁愿四倍速看番也不愿弃掉么..四倍速看番能体会到多少东西呢..</span><br><br>超级纠结..<span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">要不干脆脱宅吧</span>","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211998.jpg","floor":"#10","id":"1356399","time":"2018-6-18 01:58","userId":"211998","userName":"秘则为花","userSign":"(人啊，你曾经作为人活过吗？)","message":"我觉得，一般到此为止，就要考虑学一门理论了。毕竟经验现象是无穷的，我们有时需要一种抽象的把握。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#10-1","id":"1356404","time":"2018-6-18 02:11","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"","message":"有道理..世界过于复杂..人类了解世界还是需要简化聚合成概念.."},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#10-2","id":"1356513","time":"2018-6-18 13:41","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"","message":"到了一定的阶段发现自己已经不能不去了解经验和现象后面的东西了。<br>不去尝试理解其中的本质而继续接受这些直观经验，我忍不了。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/20/202091.jpg","floor":"#11","id":"1356401","time":"2018-6-18 02:01","userId":"av814867167","userName":"总得做点什么","userSign":"","message":"我三年前也有你这想法","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/39/94/399498.jpg","floor":"#11-1","id":"1356452","time":"2018-6-18 09:44","userId":"399498","userName":"Q","userSign":"","message":"现在是不是没感觉了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/20/202091.jpg","floor":"#11-2","id":"1356525","time":"2018-6-18 14:52","userId":"av814867167","userName":"总得做点什么","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">圆了咕咚的什么呢</span> 说: 现在是不是没感觉了</q></div>也不是，其实现在对高评分作品也有想补完的意思，只不过更加随意了。喜欢就一口气看完，不行就直接抛弃。在意后续但是看不下去就先搁着"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/14/27/142735.jpg","floor":"#12","id":"1356456","time":"2018-6-18 09:58","userId":"z55456489","userName":"ofo","userSign":"(ofo)","message":"管好吃喝拉撒就可以用睡眠时间看番了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/12.gif\" smileid=\"51\" alt=\"(bgm35)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/48/274827.jpg","floor":"#13","id":"1356466","time":"2018-6-18 10:40","userId":"kanzoso","userName":"橘花 梨樹","userSign":"","message":"我每天都在和自己说要推GAL，结果17年2月之后我一部GAL都没推完过。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/64/216493.jpg","floor":"#14","id":"1356470","time":"2018-6-18 11:02","userId":"216493","userName":"padorax","userSign":"(戯言なんだよ)","message":"不急，时间还长着啊。<br>我有这想法五六年了，还想看完所有好书。虽然我知道看不完，但就算看完了那之后干什么？所以做不到才更有意思","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/02/18/21804.jpg","floor":"#15","id":"1356475","time":"2018-6-18 11:11","userId":"mizudiwood","userName":"mizudiwood💿","userSign":"(19年小结→bgm.tv/blog/294448)","message":"计划怎么可能跟得上变化","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/30/133075.jpg","floor":"#16","id":"1356476","time":"2018-6-18 11:14","userId":"liaune","userName":"君寻","userSign":"(学会欣赏不完美)","message":"你看过了许多番剧<br>你玩过了许多游戏<br>你迷失在影视里每一道短暂的光阴<br>你品尝了迷人剧情<br>你积累了浓厚兴趣<br>你熟记故事里每一个你最爱的人名<br>却说不出这样做的原因<br>却说不出你在寻求哪一种感情<br>却说不出在什么时候它会让你动心<br>说不出爱它的意义<br>你勉强说出要寻找新的目的<br>却说不出你在寻找哪一种感情<br>你离开它<br>就是爱它的意义","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/44/14488.jpg","floor":"#16-1","id":"1356477","time":"2018-6-18 11:18","userId":"sengohanabi","userName":"線香花火","userSign":"","message":"唱出来了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/46/134645.jpg","floor":"#16-2","id":"1356515","time":"2018-6-18 13:50","userId":"pk8810","userName":"佩卡","userSign":"","message":"唱出来了+1"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/69/6912.jpg","floor":"#16-3","id":"1357139","time":"2018-6-20 21:08","userId":"6912","userName":"tora","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">[禁止发言]</span> 说: 唱出来了</q></div>+1"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/42/244287.jpg","floor":"#17","id":"1356487","time":"2018-6-18 11:36","userId":"muon","userName":"muon","userSign":"(Time is not your enemy, forever is)","message":"当你认识到某类作品都只是同一种东西的表象时，你会想去追求这个核心的抽象的东西，而同一类核心但形式不同的作品则会变得越来越枯燥无味。<br><span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">最后发现文本才是自己的最终归宿，然后当你从文本里掌握了一套理论时，看什么作品都感觉是在二次消费，Time consuming，于是变得更加的内疚<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"></span>","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/41/33/413328.jpg","floor":"#18","id":"1356521","time":"2018-6-18 14:33","userId":"himenotowa","userName":"姬野永远","userSign":"(看看)","message":"说起来我特别佩服黄油大佬<br>文本量那么大 玩个几百部需要多少时间啊！","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/56/295606.jpg","floor":"#19","id":"1356566","time":"2018-6-18 16:47","userId":"295606","userName":"absurd","userSign":"(炸雞漢堡)","message":"和吃遍天下美食一個道理<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/48/54847.jpg","floor":"#20","id":"1356569","time":"2018-6-18 17:02","userId":"sha1360","userName":"Pnyuu🌟","userSign":"(世界の殼を破られば、我らは生まれずに死んでいく ... ...)","message":"我脆皮鸭还没看够  我还不能死<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br>前几天突然觉得自己要是能生在世界末日前二十年就好了  可以了解完人类历史然后马上嗝屁","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/16/79/167918.jpg","floor":"#20-1","id":"1356664","time":"2018-6-18 22:19","userId":"jszjwzx","userName":"smallcat","userSign":"","message":"<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">活着的动力之一是想着“不行万一我要死了那个b（代指一堆太监，不一一列举）突然复出写续作了那我不就亏了”。。。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/16/79/167918.jpg","floor":"#21","id":"1356667","time":"2018-6-18 22:21","userId":"jszjwzx","userName":"smallcat","userSign":"(其实世上本没有资源帝，伸手伸得多了，也便成了资源帝 ... ...)","message":"<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">“吾生也有涯，而知也无涯。以有涯随无涯，殆已！”<br>一想到还有那么多作品没看完，就会想着一定要好好活下去啊。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/23/33/233376.jpg","floor":"#22","id":"1356670","time":"2018-6-18 22:26","userId":"xhy24825","userName":"罪のM豆","userSign":"(《2001》天下第一！)","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q>这一年不断的看，玩，现在越来越感觉到，时间有限，人的创意是无限的……</q></div>我不看动画了，JOJO！<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/41/33/413328.jpg","floor":"#22-1","id":"1356709","time":"2018-6-19 00:01","userId":"himenotowa","userName":"姬野永远","userSign":"","message":"楼主：“除非超越人类！” 突然变得很有画面感<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/23/41/234127.jpg","floor":"#23","id":"1356674","time":"2018-6-18 22:31","userId":"234127","userName":"eden","userSign":"","message":"是这样，我早上还觉得日本动漫怎么那么垃圾，下午一波侏罗纪世界我就重新发现二次元真好","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/55/255587.jpg","floor":"#24","id":"1356745","time":"2018-6-19 09:57","userId":"sudekidesu","userName":"sudekidesu","userSign":"(のんびり、のんびり〜)","message":"两年前开始，我决定再也不追新番，每个季度都补上个季度的番<br>然后我发现并看不完<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br>现在，我是每个季度都补上上上个季度的番<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/15/42/154295.jpg","floor":"#25","id":"1356748","time":"2018-6-19 10:15","userId":"fuurouta","userName":"苍辉","userSign":"","message":"想看的越看越多","sub":[]}]